## ðŸš€ How to Use

### Option 1: Direct Upload (Easy)
1. Download the ZIP of this repository.
2. Go to your Shopify Admin > Online Store > Themes > Upload Theme.
3. Upload and publish it.

### Option 2: Shopify CLI
1. Install [Shopify CLI](https://shopify.dev/docs/themes/tools/cli)
2. Clone this repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/shopify-painting-store-theme.git
   cd shopify-painting-store-theme
